## ThreadID.fromString() method

fromString parses an ID-encoded string and returns an ID object. For IDV1, an ID-encoded string is primarily a multibase string: <multibase-type-code><base-encoded-string> The base-encoded string represents a: <version><variant><random-number>

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
static fromString(v: string | Uint8Array): ThreadID;
```

## Parameters

|  Parameter | Type | Description |
|  --- | --- | --- |
|  v | string \| Uint8Array | The input encoded Thread ID. |

<b>Returns:</b>

ThreadID
